    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and is looking for a new home. You won't find another one this clean. Come take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
