      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it is in truly pristine, mint condition. No scratches, no dings, and it still has that fresh feel inside. It drives like an absolute dream! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. Drop me a message if you have any questions or want to come by and take a look. Can't wait to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
