    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a true time-capsule specimen for the discerning purist. This example features the high-revving S54 power plant with razor-sharp individual throttle body response. The double-VANOS system has been fully serviced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance to ensure internal longevity. The chassis remains structurally pristine with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry optimized by Bilstein dampers. Drive is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Every panel retains original paint depth, and the undercarriage is free of fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a mechanically sorted, high-performance icon ready for a collection.",
